data.title: American Vacuum Society's Prairie Chapter selects Diao for Early Career Award
data.meta_description: American Vacuum Society's Prairie Chapter selects Diao for Early Career Award
data.text:
Congratulations to Assistant Professor of Chemical and Biomolecular Engineering Ying Diao, who was recently selected to receive the 2019 American Vacuum Societyâ€™s Prairie Chapter Early Career Award.
